data.description: Fantastic corner lot property we know you are going to love.  Spacious living room and good sized bedrooms with ceiling fans. Neutral color paint throughout.  The kitchen offers tile backsplash, granite countertops, and upgraded cabinetry with plenty of storage space.  No maintenance landscaping in the backyard with covered patio and room to relax, entertain, and play.  The neighborhood is well maintained and quiet.  Ideal starter home for you first time buyers.  It is also perfect as a rental if you're looking for an investment.  Hurry and come take a look while you still can! You won't be disappointed.
